and humane manner. Or, again, it describes best psychotherapeutic practice. Alchemy is read not as a medium for "personal growth", but optimal co-existence with the natural world. It is an eco-logical rather than ego-logical project with deep aesthetic concerns (education of the senses in close noticing) and political intentions (a democracy of worldly things). The book echoes post-Freudian developments in psychoanalysis that avoid the mysticism of symbol systems to work rather with everyday signs and linguistic registers such as embodied metaphors, keeping the focus on known and sensed phenomena rather than abstractions.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / General.2bisacsh  aalchemy.  alanguage.  ametaphor.  apsychotherapy.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2023 Part 1z978311117578208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishz978311131929208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary Studies 2023 Englishz978311131918608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary Studies 2023z9783111318264oZDB-23-DSP0 cEPUBz97831111599040 cprintz978311115477040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311115736840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783111157368423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783111157368/original  a978-3-11-117578-2  DG Plus DeG Package 2023 Part 1b2023  a978-3-11-131918-6  EBOOK PACKAGE Literary Studies 2023 Englishb2023  a978-3-11-131929-2  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishb2023  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LT  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-d